{
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "inspired_by": "nexu-io/open-design § first-party atom catalog. Atoms are the atomic capabilities a skill (or phase) composes into a pipeline; plugins reference them by stable id rather than reimplementing the prompt fragment.",
